## Third-Party Content (Games Folder)

The `Games/` folder contains references to third-party games that are
not owned by the Psy-Lens Project.

- No ownership or license over those games is claimed
- All rights remain with their respective creators
- Inclusion is strictly for reference, critique, and discussion

Any reviews or notes written in this repository reflect personal
analysis and do not transfer ownership of the referenced works.

---

## Assets and References

Any third-party assets or references included in this repository must:

- Clearly state their original creator
- Include the original license
- Follow the rules defined in the `Workflows/` documentation

Assets with restrictive licenses may be excluded from redistribution
or limited to internal reference only.

